    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Sports or recreational activities that are pursued out of doors in an area of open land free of woods and buildings; often used for sports in which the field is marked and divided in a specific way for a particular sport. Also used for sports that have traditionally been played in outdoor areas, but the arenas and associated fields have been covered with large roofs.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>English</Note_Language>
        <Note_Contributors>
          <Note_Contributor>
            <Contributor_id>10000000/VP</Contributor_id>
          </Note_Contributor>
        </Note_Contributors>
        <Note_Sources>
